isVerticalDevMode

public static boolean isVerticalDevMode()
This is an applcore internal method used by the level picker dialog. The method return true is the "ORA_FND_VERTICAL_DEV_MODE" profile option has been set. When set only the IndustryCC level is set as the tip in the MDSSession.SessionOptions.
